1. Added `pointer-events-none` to the container div that holds the floating icons:
 ```css
 className="fixed right-4 bottom-36 lg:right-8 lg:top-52 h-32 w-[210px] z-40 hidden lg:block pointer-events-none"
 ```

2. Added `pointer-events-auto` to each individual button container:
